v1|craft-orchestration-index
=ROUTING
in-progress story|AskUser: Continue? â†’ story-continue
planning cycle|All ready? â†’ cycle-start | Still planning? â†’ cycle-design
pending requests|AskUser: Review? â†’ /craft Step 5b
status:planning (no chunks)|plan-chunks first
status:ready|story-implement
in backlog|cycle-assign first
mid-chunk (CHUNK>0)|Continue implement loop
validation FAILED (test)|test-fix (via story-implement)
validation FAILED (build/lint)|refine-chunk (via story-implement)
all stories complete|cycle-complete
post-cycle|analyze (QA,UX,Creative,Style)
known bug or small tweak to shipped work (no active story)|craft:adhoc (no story needed)
deferral marker in user utterance ("later"/"don't let me forget"/"side note"/etc.)|inline-mention /craft:notebook (NOT AskUserQuestion); on accept invoke silently with session-context body+tags
lifecycle verb + named/deictic ref|graduate=inline-offer with named referent / done=AUQ confirmation always (even at HIGH conf - asymmetric failure visibility); LOW=no action
unsettled visual direction (visual change circling, no committed look / directions rejected in a row)|inline-mention mockup offer (NOT AskUserQuestion); on accept â†’ craft:mockup, session context seeds the brief
=LOOP
Per chunk 1..N:
1.create-checkpoint.sh [story] [chunk]
2.INVOKE implementer via Task (NEVER implement directly)
3.INVOKE chunk-validator via Task (haiku)
4.PASSED:complete-chunk.shâ†’next chunk | FAILED:Read commands/references/validate-fix-loop.mdâ†’fix(Skill)â†’re-validate
5.Loop to 1
After all: chunk-validator finalâ†’claims-auditâ†’self-critiqueâ†’complete-story.sh
=CHAINS
story-implementâ†’[checkpointâ†’implementer(Task)â†’chunk-validator(haiku)â†’pass:complete-chunk.shâ†’fail:Read commands/references/validate-fix-loop.mdâ†’fix(Skill)â†’re-validate]Ă—Nâ†’chunk-validator finalâ†’claims-auditâ†’complete-story.sh
test-fixâ†’triageâ†’HAND BACK TO story-implement
refine-chunkâ†’surgical fixâ†’HAND BACK TO story-implement
cycle-designâ†’content-spark(per story)â†’creative-spark(opt)â†’design-vibeâ†’plan-chunks MODE=batch
story-newâ†’content-sparkâ†’creative-spark(opt)â†’plan-chunks
adhocâ†’classify|bug:investigateâ†’confidenceâ†’editâ†’validate|tweak:fit-checkâ†’editâ†’validateâ†’AUQ(record open until user accepts)|unsure:ask user
notebookâ†’capture | notebookâ†’captureâ†’done (conversational, AUQ always) | notebookâ†’captureâ†’graduate(conversational)â†’story-new (pre-fills spark; idea flagged graduated / todo closed done+graduated_to - graduate accept is the one consent, no done-AUQ)
=RULES
!implement chunks directlyâ€”ALWAYS invoke implementer via Task
!validate directlyâ€”invoke chunk-validator via Task (validate-chunk skill is manual-only)
!edit .state/.global-state directlyâ€”use transition scripts
!run_in_background for test/typecheck/lint/buildâ€”must be synchronous
!override FAILED verdictâ€”FAILED means FAILED
!present story content from memoryâ€”Read file fresh
!batch concernsâ€”surface each via AskUserQuestion
!run a craft flow from memory when its reference Read failsâ€”"File does not exist" (a tool fact) means: resolve against the plugin root stated above, retry once
!hard-wall on a Read that fails twiceâ€”disclose in ONE line (file, expected path, plugin version from .claude-plugin/plugin.json; "reinstall may fix; if not it's a craft bugâ€”this message is the report: github.com/drobins25/craft/issues"), then AskUserQuestion: continue best-effort | stop
+checkpoint before each chunk (create-checkpoint.sh)
+transition scripts for state changes
+breadcrumb before nested skill invocation
+clean up breadcrumb on ALL exit paths
!stop after chunk/story completesâ€”continue to next chunk or next story
!conflate notebook todos with TaskCreateâ€”different lifetimes (notebook=persistent across sessions, TaskCreate=ephemeral, /craft:adhoc=act-now bug/tweak)
=SCRIPTS
start-cycle.sh [cycle]|activate,set ACTIVE_CYCLE
complete-cycle.sh|archive,clear ACTIVE_CYCLE
start-story.sh [file]|set CURRENT_STORY,CHUNK=1,status=active
complete-story.sh [file]|clear CURRENT_STORY,status=complete
complete-chunk.sh|increment CURRENT_CHUNK
create-checkpoint.sh [story] [chunk]|YAML state snapshot,no commit(commit at complete-story.sh)
update-global-state.sh KEY VAL|safe .global-state update
=STATE
.craft/.global-state|ACTIVE_CYCLE,CURRENT_STORY,PLANNING_CYCLE,RUN_MODE
.craft/cycles/{c}/.state|CURRENT_CHUNK,TOTAL_CHUNKS,CURRENT_STORY
.craft/cycles/{c}/cycle.yaml|title,goal,status(planning|ready|active|complete)
Story frontmatter:status|planningâ†’readyâ†’activeâ†’complete
.craft/.continuation|breadcrumb for nested skills(30min TTL,one-shot)
.craft/settings.yaml|default_mode,parallel planning
.craft/design/locked.md|locked decisions(enforced by validation)
.craft/design/tokens.yaml|design tokens(enforced by style-analyzer)
.craft/fixes/*.md|adhoc fix records(category,root cause,validation)
.craft/tweaks/tweak-*.md|tweak records(surface,kind,attempts,verbatim reactions;open until user accepts)
.craft/.active-fix|safety marker for in-progress adhoc work(session-start clears)
